      <title>交易员在政策决定前数小时抛售押注英国央行降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/traders-doubt-whether-boe-will-cut-interest-rates-in-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在英格兰银行官员公布政策的几个小时前，投资者正在迅速平仓英国央行进一步宽松政策的押注。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/traders-doubt-whether-boe-will-cut-interest-rates-in-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 09:52:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国家庭用水进一步紧张，水费或将上涨 36%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/uk-water-bills-to-rise-36-over-5-years-as-households-squeezed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[未来五年，英格兰和威尔士的水费将上涨 36%，这将给已经饱受水价上涨困扰的家庭带来更大压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/uk-water-bills-to-rise-36-over-5-years-as-households-squeezed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 07:19:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
